margin: 0 0 20px 0;">Hope you had a great weekend, and happy Father&#8217;s=
 Day to all the Not Boring dads.</p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: =
16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0;">This weekend, we visited my p=
arents at the beach to celebrate Father&#8217;s Day and my dad&#8217;s birt=
hday (happy birthday, dad!). On Sunday morning, my mom asked what I was wri=
ting about, and I told her I had no idea. So she said, &#8220;OK, let&#8217=
