ht: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em>We had no idea that y=
our life was going to be what it is today when you were born. You write a n=
ewsletter, from home, and send it to people all over the world, on the inte=
rnet.&#160;</em></p><p style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-heigh=
t: 26px; margin: 0 0 20px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em>I remember when I came=
 back from maternity leave, Donna [my mom&#8217;s teammate at Bell Atlantic=
] told me about the internet for the first time. We were mainly worried abo=
ut coin-operated payphones at the time. We thought one day there would be p=
icture phones, but we had no idea what the internet would mean.</em></p><p =
style=3D"color: #404040; font-size: 16px; line-height: 26px; margin: 0 0 20=
px 0; margin-left: 20px;"><em>If technology is moving even faster now than =
